parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag did not deploy in a crash
airbag warning light is on
airbag malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The TAKATA airbag recall has resulted in a prolonged and frustrating experience for many owners, leaving them with a sense of insecurity and uncertainty about the safety of their vehicles.
symptoms: Delayed or lack of notification about the recall
unavailability of replacement parts
inability to schedule a repair
lack of communication from the manufacturer or dealer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The grinding noise when accelerating can lead to a loss of control or an accident, potentially causing injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Grinding noise when accelerating from 0-35 mph
noise noticed during diagnostic testing but not resolved.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the drive shaft can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or strand the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
the drive shaft fractures
the vehicle is unable to move
the clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the vehicle makes a loud thud or noise
the vehicle drifts or loses control.

the vehicle drifts or loses control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the EPS system can cause the steering to become stiff and unpredictable, leading to loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The power steering cuts out intermittently

causing the steering to become stiff and heavy; the EPS indicator light may flash momentarily; the radio may cut out simultaneously; the steering wheel may lock up in a turned position; the vehicle may veer into oncoming traffic.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the airbag light to flash, the radio to malfunction, and the steering to lose power, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The airbag light flashes; the electrical system shuts off; the radio flashes on and off; the steering loses power; the headlights shut off; the vehicle becomes difficult to control.
